-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
                        Architecture
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

I have implemented the buttons and widjets using the java swing frameworks.
This has allowed me to create a class for every widget or button which is then
used by the main class.


How to compile: 
---------------
1. run javac Main.java
2. run java Main